profile:
In Depth Energy Inspections provides full service home and cottage inspections; thermal imaging is always included.
Complete home energy audits with air leakage testing are the best way to identify heat loss, moisture intrusion, and ways to save money and improve comfort year round.
Seller's inspections provide a great way to market your home as Move-In-Certified to potential buyers, document repairs you've made, and disclose any concerns that could otherwise delay negotiations.
Green certifications are available too.
Call 705-455-2004 to schedule now.
